Put this directory somewhere. Edit installnvvj and change
line 27 to the directory where these files are placed.
From VJ, set an appdir to this directory.
Do the following

xhost +
su
cd <vjunit>
./installnvvj

You can also run a cronjob, such as
50 09 * * * /home/vnmr1/vjunit/vjunit_vj3/installnvvj
Make sure the "xhost +" has been done.
